description: Cline Scientific AB engages in the development and marketing of biomedical products for stem cell and cancer research. The company is headquartered in Moelndal, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2015-03-30. The company develops and markets nanotechnology products for biomedical research. The company is specialized in providing gradient surface technology to life science applications. Its product range includes surfaces for use in stem cell- and cancer research, customized nanoparticles for biomedical applications, and gradients for in-vitro applications.
name: Cline Scientific AB
